   Why is LINUX so great?
-    New features in LINUX 2.2/2.3
+  New features in LINUX
+    The 2.2 kernel series
+    The 2.3 kernel series
 Unix foundations (10)
	:
 Network Devices (20)
+  Telecommunications Links
+    Protocols
+      Parallel Link Internet Protocol (PLIP)
+      Serial Link Internet Protocol (SLIP)
+      Serial Link Relay Protocol (SLiRP)
+      Point to Point Protocol (PPP)
+    Interfaces
+      The 'Null Modem' Connection
+      Analogue Modems (POTS)
+      Integrated Services Digital Network (ISDN)
+      Asynchronous Digital Subscriber Line (ADSL)
+  Wired networking
+    Ethernet
+    Token Ring
+  Wireless Networking
+    Amateur Packet Radio (AX.25)
+    WaveLAN
 SCSI Devices (20)
	:
 Audio Devices
-  DSP
+  Digital Signal Processors (DSP)
   Synthesisers
	:
